õJulia Hinchcliffe 1975-2010
"I thought of you today but that is nothing new.
I thought of you yesterday and days before that too.
I think of you in silence, I often speak your name.
Your Laughter fills the sunlight and echoes through the rain.
Your memory is a keepsake from which we'll never part
God has you in his keeping, I have you in my heart.""Ņ
ļGood night sweet Prince and may
flights of angels sing you to your rest.
Thank you for being my friend.
JD

Neil Young
11th April 1961 - 15th July 2019
You were our sunshine
Ali, Izzie, Charlotte, Family & Friends
Forever in our hearts"¾
